social_posts.post_text: 2022 was a super busy year. We traveled to some really cool places this year. I hope you all have a healthy and prosperous 2023. What was your favorite part of 2022?

It’s 2023!! Time to try new things, achieve new goals, and live our best lives. Hope everyone has a prosperous, healthy New Year filled with love, laughs and great times. I’m trying out some new looks for the new year. Let me know which one I should go with. 😁

If you travel through Newark Airport, you should know about this mystery fee that gets added to purchases made at the snack/convenience shoots. It’s new and a lot of the stores don’t have any signage about it. No where does it really explain what this fee is used for. Buyer beware!

Have you ever walked into a store, grabbed something and just walked right out? That’s exactly what I just did here. While in Seattle, I visited the Amazon Go Store. Check out what happens when I take what I want and leave.
I went to Voodoo Donuts while in the Portland, Oregon area. They make outrageous donuts that are delicious! What’s your favorite donut flavor?
It’s been a fun couple of weeks. Now it’s time to finish off the best of 7 series with a win. Tomorrow night, it’s Escalera de la Muerte on #aewdynamite
#DeathTriangle were the longest reigning @aew World Trios Champions. This is not the end, only the beginning.

Celebrated Manchego’s 3rd birthday yesterday. He’s such an amazing little man. He was super excited to have his peanut butter and banana. That’s what I always give him on his b-day. He loves his new toy and played plenty with his brother Cooper. It’s safe to say he had a great day. Pugs rock! #pugsofinstagram #pugs
Had fun walking the Santa Monica Pier when we were in Los Angeles last week. Who else has been there?
@rjcity @dashakuret run down everything that you’ll see on tonight’s #aewdynamite  We are live from Lexington, Kentucky.
It’s almost February, is this acceptable? What’s next, a St. Patrick’s Day one? ☘️
Pugs love belly rubs don’t they? Does your dog enjoy them as much as Manchego does? Let me know.

#aewdynamite is live from Dayton, OH. It’s going to be a great show filled with action packed matches. Join us at 8pm EST on TNT.  Who’s going to be the TNT Champion after tonight? Will @jonmoxley beat @hangmanadampage ? Can @la_redvelvet beat TBS Champ @jadecargill ?

So grateful to be able to spend time with my abuelo, who is 96 years old. He still so sharp and witty. He’s one of the best story tellers, I’ve ever met. He made me laugh today when he told me that it’s ok to work hard,  as long as they are paying you. 😝 He’s awesome.
Had a fun day in Puerta Plata, Dominican Republic. It was the first port stop on @virginvoyages #scarletlady What’s your favorite cruise port? #cruises
Calling all foodies. Here’s a little bit of what I’ve been having to eat on the cruise. #cruise #cruiselife

Had a crazy flight situation yesterday on my to #aewdynamite The airplane had an Issue. I’m ok thank goodness, and I made to it to El Paso. 🙏
He initially wouldn’t even look at me when I asked him if he attacked and broke the Heartbreak Kid.  I knew he was a Bret fan.
Took a walk on the top deck of the #scarletlady The sky is a little different in the middle of the Atlantic. 😜
Tonight #aewdynamite comes to from Laredo, TX. @dashakuret and I run down the card. We are goi g to have a Texas Death Tornado Tag Match! Tune into @tbsnetwork at 8pm est.

It was a busy weekend. Saturday was Icons of Wrestling. It’s was really great connecting with fellow Pro Wrestling fans. It was also great seeing @realmelina who I hadn’t seen in almost 10 years! Sunday was the QVC Today’s Special Value. It was a long, but successful day. On to another great week.

They are the only tag team ever to have held the @aew tag team titles, Trios Championships, Impact Tag Team Titles AAA Tag Team Championships and now @ringofhonor tag team titles. Last night my Lucha Brothers were victorious against @realqtmarshall and @true_will_hobbs at #aewbotb

Happy birthday to my little Cooper. I am pretty sure that he turns 5 today. The reason that I’m not 100% sure is because that’s the information I was given when I rescued him. I wasn’t sure what to expect when I did that almost a year ago. I remember seeing a Facebook post of him crying and shaking, and I knew that I had to help him. Little did I know how quickly I’d fall in love with him. He is so spunky and loving. He trusts me so much and loves attention. I gave him some peanut butter and banana for his B-day, as I’ve always done with my other fur-babies. He was one happy birthday boy.

I rescued a pug yesterday. The decision was nerve racking because I’ve never had three dogs before. I wasn’t sure how Manchego and Cooper would like having another brother around. At first, they were just full of energy trying to figure things out. Now they seem to be getting used to each other and are constantly playing. It fills my heart with joy having another pug. Super grateful to have little Benny join our family.

With all the excitement about rescuing Benny on Thursday: I could not forget that it’s been one year exactly that I rescued Cooper. I didn’t know what I was getting myself into. I recall seeing a video of him on facebook looking so nervous about being surrendered. My gut just told me that I had to help him. Always listen to your gut! The year has flown by and I could not love this little guy anymore. He’s quirky, fun and full of personality. They say that a rescue dog never forgets what you did for them. Cooper seems to show me that every day. Happy gotcha day Cooper! ❤️ #jackchi

One of the things that I love about @aew is being able to have my family experience it. Last night, my family had a chance to see Dynamite live. I am so grateful for their support. They helped me get to where I am today.

Today marks 7 years since I began on air at QVC. I’ll never forget that 3am airing with @maryqvc It was wild! Very grateful to be doing something that I enjoy very much. The hosts and other guests make it so much fun. Not to mention the other great folks behind the scenes who work so hard everyday. Proud to represent @hp #maythe4thbewithyou a day early. 😁

Bermuda is one of my favorite places on earth. Sailing on @norwegiancruiseline Pearl has been so much fun. We are docked here for 2 night and 3 days. What a great way to see the island. I highly recommend you out Bermuda on your bucket list if you haven’t been here. What’s one place you would recommend that you feel the same about? #cruisenorwegian #bermuda #cruise

What an amazing few days it’s been on board of the @norwegiancruiseline Pearl. There’s so much to see and enjoy in Bermuda. The sights are amazing, and the people are as warm as the climate. Sometimes you just have to get a way and reconnect with places that you love to recharge. That’s what I did and I can’t wait to go back. #cruisenorwegian #vacation #bermuda
It doesn’t matter how many times you see @reyfenixmx wrestle, he always amazing you with what he can do. #animo #luchabrothers #roh
Cooper and Manchego have been working as a tag team lately to battle the new kid on the block, Benny. Every day is like a battle royale on #aewdynamite #dogsofinstagram
The best tag team in the Universe successfully defended their @ringofhonor tag team titles this week on #aewdynamite

I’ve been to San Diego a handful of times, but have never seen this side. Yesterday I went to go see the Old Point Loma Lighthouse. It’s located in an amazing national park. I highly recommend going. I could have spent the entire day there just starring at the cliffs and ocean. What a great day it was.

Had a great time @super7sandiego I am a huge fan of their toys. As a collector (especially if 80’s cartoons) I love their figures. I have a ton of their toys. So much so that I created a wall of just their reaction figures. The store is super cool because they have other great items like t-shirts, glasses and more. They have two locations; this one and one in San Francisco.I ’ll definitely be back when we return to either city.
@luchalibreaaa @aew #luchalibre #luchabrothers #penta_zero_miedo #zeromiedo #penta #animo #aaa #AEW #wrestling #champion #luchaaaa #prowrestling
Last night on #aewrampage my Lucha Bros teamed up again with Bandido, forming the Super Lucha Brothers. They defeated Big Bill, Ethan Page and Lee Moriarty. How 🔥 is this trios combination???

This Thursday will be two months since Benny joined our pack. Today, he hopped on a chair to get some sun with his big brother Manchego. Just a few minute ago, Manchego gave him a few kisses. They are currently cuddled up taking a nap together. I think that brotherly love has finally happened. Now we just need Cooper to show his little brother some love. I’ll keep you all posted. 😁
From the first @aew Pay Per View, to the first AEW Dynamite, to tonight’s debut edition of #AEWCollision. Super grateful to be here in Chicago to be a part of history.

What happens when the Spanish Announce Team @aew has a day off? Do they rest? Do they sleep in? Do they take it easy? No!! We go to karaoke and live our best lives!! What’s your go to karaoke song? #karaoke

It’s Saturday and you know what the means. It’s time for #AEWCollision @thunderrosa22 @alvaro.aew and I, always have so much fun working together. We will be calling the action in Spanish tonight starting at 8pm est on TNT.

I am proud to now also be The Hype Man for the rising star @komandercrguevara He may not have won the @ringofhonor World Championship, he won the respect of many. This is just the beginning for the commander of the skies.
We may not all be related by blood, but we are related by our love of lucha. This is a Lucha Family.

When I’m working a Today’s Special Value at QVC, I’ll have several outfit changes. The day starts at midnight and goes until 11:59pm. That means several hour long presentations throughout the course of the day. Throughout the day, I’ll take mini naps and eat to keep my energy level up. A lot of preparation goes into the day. The week before, I’m intensely getting ready. I guess it’s a lot like a pro wrestling pay per view. 😁
Could not be prouder of @komandercrguevara What a performance last night against the GOAT @chrisjerichofozzy The sky is the limit for this rising star!
We are in Calgary, Alberta, Canada. Who’s going to win the Owen Hart Foundation Tournament? We are wearing our pink and black tonight!! #aewcollision

It’s hard to put into words what returning to Calgary, Alberta, Canada meant for me. Growing up, I was fascinated by The Harts and the infamous Dungeon. It was so great to go back to a place that meant so much to me. I was overwhelmed with gratitude for the Harts, who took me in, and made me feel like a part of their family. It was a very special time in my life that I will never forget. Looking forward to going back and continuing to make new memories. Thank you Harts. Thank you to AEW for bringing me back there.
“Yeehaw! I finally made it to the Calgary Stampede!🤠 This place was amazing! From the food to the rides, everything is so much fun. I can’t wait to come back!🎉🎡🎢”

It’s always great coming back home. I used to work in this arena. I dreamed about being where I am today. Don’t give up on your dreams, they are 1000% worth it when you achieve them. Also, a very happy birthday to @thunderrosa22

While @ringofhonor #deathbeforedishonor May not have gone our way, my brothers gave their all. It’s not how many times you fall down that counts, it’s how many times you get back up. Championships will be held again.

@hijodelvikingoaaaoficial and @komandercrguevara are showing the world what they can do as a tag team. #ringofhonor #aew
What a memorable couple of weeks it’s been. From Canada to Florida and several places in between. Fun times have been had, and memories have been made.
Death Triangle is a brotherhood. The BCC has not seen the last of the Lucha Brothers. #aewdynamite
When you combine two creative sources, the possibilities are endless.

Last night, two of the best Luchadores in the world battled it out of #aewrampage They left in all in the ring in the spirit of competition. What you didn’t see on TV was what happened after the match. Rey Fenix took his mask off and gave it to Komander. This is the ultimate act of respect and appreciation that you can get in Lucha. What a match and what great human beings. I am so grateful to be their Hype Man, and more importantly their friend.
We are about to make history at Wembly Stadium!! Penta is bringing the heat tonight for Stadium Stampede!! #aewallin

Still can’t process that we performed in front of over 80,000 fans at Wembly Stadium last night. Sharing this moment with friends who worked their butts off to get to this here was awesome. I can’t wait to do it all over again next year!!

Proud to announce that I have created a Lucha Libre coloring book. It’s called Color Me Lucha and is now available on Amazon. You can search for it directly or find the link in my bio. If you pick it up, please post about it. I’d love to see you with the book and I hope that you love it.

Last night was one of the most memorable nights of my life. I began my pro wrestling career at @pennstate . As a student, I used to go to every pro wrestling show at the @jordancenter Now I can officially say, that I have wrestled at the very arena that I graduated from. Beyond grateful to those who were involved and made it happen. What was extra special to me was being able to tell the fans not to give up on their dreams. My goal has always been to inspire people to pursue theirs. I hope that my story proves that anyone can make it. #wearepennstate #aew
Don’t mess with my Lucha Brothers or I will bring the Hype!! #aewrampage

Congratulations to the NEW #AEW International Champion, @ReyFenixMx!

#ANDNEW

@reyfenixmx is an example of what happens when you never quit, you never give up and you keep striving towards your goals. I am so unbelievably proud of what my Lucha Brother has accomplished. He has been knocked down many times, but like a phoenix he always finds a way to rise above. Congrats to the NEW @aew International Champion.
If you are sleeping on Penta, you can’t possibly be serious.
My Lucha Brothers went out last night on #aewdynamite and showed the world why they are the best. It doesn’t matter whether it’s singles or tag matches, they always bring the 🔥🔥😎
Penta says he wants you to have Zero Miedo!!!

Tonight is #aewwrestledream so it’s apropos that I realize one as well. This is my first ever @shopaew t-shirt. I designed this shirt and am beyond grateful to now be able to share it with all of you. #aew

I designed this t-shirt with inspiration of one of my favorite cartoons growing up. The lion was also my favorite animal. It symbolizes courage. Growing up, when times were tough, that was a reminder for me to stay strong. I also happen to be a @pennstate Nittany Lion. So it was only fitting that this symbol represents who I’ve become. I’ll never take things like this for granted. I am so grateful for these amazing life goals and dreams that have come true. Whatever you want to do in life, don’t give up. If you stick with it long enough, and work to make it happen, someday you will realize that the struggle is worth it
And still your @aew International Champion @reyfenixmx !! What a match last night against Nick Jackson on the 4th anniversary of #aewdynamite
#modaymotivation brought to you by the greatest tag team in the universe… The Lucha Brothers.

Spaghetti ice cream. Those are two words I thought I’d never say, let alone eat. I discovered this ice cream shop in Cape Coral, Florida. If you are in the area, make sure to stop by @holymolyicecream to try one of their unique and fun creations. Is there anything better than #icecream ?

When I find something I Like, I just have to share it. For the longest is been taking vitamins that we're easy to forget to take. They were not convenient and we're expensive. I saw an ad for these on IG and figured I'd give them a shot. They are super easy to take with me on the go. So I made this video,  in hopes that it helps some of you. I wrote the company and they gave me a discount code to share. I've put that in my bio in case you want to check it out.

What a year it was! 2023 was a bit of a blur because so much happened. Death Triangle started the year with the @aew Trios Championships. The Lucha Brothers won the @ringofhonor tag team Championships. @reyfenixmx won the International Championship. Teamed up with an amazing Luchador in @komandercrguevara 

I rescued a clumsy loveably pug named Benny. 
Got an AEW Trading Card and T-shirt this year. 
AEW had a record breaking All In show at Wembley Stadium, and I got to perform in front of over 80,000 fans.

Returned to Calgary, Alberta, Canada with AEW, which is where I initially trained. I also returned to Penn State and had a match in the same arena that I graduated from. What a wild ride it was!! Super grateful for an awesome year. Looking to continue to grow in 2024. 

What are your goals this year?

Happy New Year!!!🎊🎈🎆
Behind every great champion, there is a Hype Man.

I love being able to work with people who give their all each and every time. That’s exactly who @komandercrguevara is. He is constantly striving to be better each and every day. The sky is the limit for him. 🫡 #aew
